A shimmering row of pave diamonds splits, continuing up the base of each prong to meet at a subtle point before descending into a diamond-studded bridge. The setting boasts glittering brilliance from all angles, making your center stone appear larger while a slimming silhouette elongates the finger.

title: The Low Profile Kamellie Set With A 2.5 Carat Radiant Lab Diamond
description: Set with intricate pave diamonds, The Low Profile Kamellie blends the tastefully modern with a timeless classic. The hidden halo ensures there is sparkle coming in from every angle, highlighting your center stone and making it appear larger. The delicate design flatters the finger, while its low profile makes it practical for even the busiest hands.
